**Crowd Seeker** | Townsfolk Investigative
__Basics__
The Crowd Seeker may investigate up to 3 players each night by guessing their roles. Each correct guess is confirmed.
__Details__
The Crowd Seeker can select up to three different players each night, and guess for each of them what their role could be. All guesses have to be made at the same time, and all correct ones will be confirmed. 
The Crowd Seeker is affected by weak disguises and obstructions. The Crowd Seekerâ€™s seeking is an immediate ability.
